{"type": "article", "id": 14290, "title": "滑动方凳", "description": "", "date": "2015-09-02T07:21:15Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 10, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606060003297NwTLqEmMZ9AKiPg.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t这把方凳是可以滑开的，也可以当咖啡桌。它的侧边源于阿拉伯国家黎巴嫩的拱形建筑，拉开方凳，侧面依然维持了优雅的弧度。用木材制作而没有任何别的装饰，突出了它的结构。设计师是出生于黎巴嫩的年轻夫妇，他们想要以此提醒人们对老建筑的关注。<a href=\"http://www.squad-design.com/pages/stools%20exhibition/charbel_and_stephanie_arcus.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里可以查看更多信息。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141913vIXZe3dpo9WHVnsF.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"618\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57222222\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141913Wo7kQaeDHORy0Y9A.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"343\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141914AWCgqGI3ciHBw0oR.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"343\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.57166667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160726141914XtcWQnJ1aj6wgZC8.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"600\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n\n"}